Revision history for Alien::libwebsockets

0.03    2026-04-04
        - Libev support now optional (auto-detected at build time).
        - Auto-detect latest libwebsockets release from GitHub.

0.02    2026-03-30
        - Improved cross-platform support and build determinism.

0.01    2026-02-20
        - Initial release.
        - Bundles libwebsockets 4.3.3.
        - Enabled extensions, zlib, and libev support.
        - Provides has_extensions() for detecting extension support.
